# This is the global gitignore file for all of my projects
# You need to set up your git configuration to point to this file:
# git config --global core.excludesfile <PATH-TO-THIS-FILE>

# This file ignores OS / software configuration files that are not
# specific to a project, e.g., VS Code and JetBrains IDE settings.

